### Run Monthly Segmentation - Default (no force update)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hcm/engine/customer-segmentation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{}

### Run Monthly Segmentation - With Force Update
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hcm/engine/customer-segmentation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "force_update": true
}

### Run Monthly Segmentation - Explicit No Force Update
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hcm/engine/customer-segmentation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "force_update": false
}
